uniol.apt.adt

Class Node<G extends IGraph<G,E,N>,E extends IEdge<G,E,N>,N extends INode<G,E,N>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uniol.apt.adt.extension.Extensible
      • uniol.apt.adt.Node<G,E,N>
  • Type Parameters:
    G - The type of the graph.
    E - The type of the edge itself.
    N - The type of the nodes.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IExtensible, INode<G,E,N>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Node, State

    public abstract class Node<G extends IGraph<G,E,N>,E extends IEdge<G,E,N>,N extends INode<G,E,N>>
extends Extensible
implements INode<G,E,N>
    An implementation of the interface INode for just delegating the pre- and postset methodes to the graph of the type G.
    Author:
    Dennis-Michael Borde, Manuel Gieseking
    See Also:
    INode
